{"tid":2363552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食外賣食到崩牙","createTime":"2021-01-12T09:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T09:46:46.000Z","uid":366484,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"36cb07e6980972bb50e56bc6ca42a6ffb612f070","tid":2363552,"uid":366484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:40:15.000Z","msg":"頭先叫左份茶記炒飯外賣<br />\n翻屋企食左差唔多一半果陣咬到舊硬硬地嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嘔出黎發現係好似石仔咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後照鏡望左陣，好似崩左兩隻大牙，一隻上排一隻下排，痛到pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打電話翻去個茶記同個老細對質，個老細話可以退翻個飯，然後叫我去睇完牙再翻去同佢商量，唔知有無得claim翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家唔知點算，係咪咁就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恆齒黎架屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b17d0cddfd063ceb742907bfc5c1ad344b3fa3","tid":2363552,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"輕微就補牙<br />\n嚴重就剝牙再植牙"}]}